        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Haplotype networks for cytochrome oxidase c subunit 1. A, Nereimyra aphroditoides. B, Nereimyra punctata. C, Nereimyra woodsholea. Each bar across a line connecting two specimens denotes one mutation. Numbers correspond to specimens numbers in Table 1, and letters indicate origin (G, Greenland; M, Middle Atlantic Bight; N, Norway; S, Sweden; V, Svalbard)." ;
